    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. This example delivers a visceral, naturally aspirated experience with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a mechanical limited-slip differential. The chassis remains composed thanks to reinforced subframe mounting points and a refreshed suspension geometry with upgraded bushings. While it exhibits minor cosmetic patina expected of its age, the mechanical vitals are robust, offering the communicative steering and balanced weight distribution that define this analog performance icon.",
