      "description": "This vehicle is a standout example of pride of ownership, offering a perfect balance of reliability and aesthetic appeal. The exterior paint retains a brilliant luster, though a close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel arch\u2014typical of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the leather seats are firm and free of punctures, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every feature, from the panoramic sunroof to the heated seats and navigation system, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio. We recently performed a multi-point inspection, which confirmed the suspension is tight and the transmission shifts seamlessly. With 75% tread remaining on the Michelin tires and a fresh oil service just completed, this car is ready for the road with no immediate maintenance required.",
